    "title": "Ananda in the Himalayas is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Lead)",
    "description": "We at Ananda in the Himalayas are looking for an experienced Guest Relations Manager based out of Nagpur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Ananda in the Himalayas:\nAnanda in the Himalayas is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ananda in the Himalayas!",
